OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud
OL,6,Fthickening through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight. Winds also strengthening,
OL,8,Fwith upland gales likely, and perhaps
OL,9,Fsome rain across northern hills.
OL,10,FLikely staying frost free.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FCloudy morning, with some
OL,13,Fparts dry, but also outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Fpossible. Occasionally heavy and
OL,15,Fblustery rain then moves southeast
OL,16,Fduring the afternoon, clearing North
OL,17,FYorkshire into the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
