OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCold and
OL,6,Fbreezy Friday with brighter spells and
OL,7,Foccasional showers, wintry over hills.
OL,8,FLess cold Saturday, but still the odd
OL,9,Fshower likely. Further rain and strong
OL,10,Fwinds spreading east Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
